'''OGLE-2006-BLG-109Lb'''是一顆距離地球約4920光年的[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]，在天球上位於[[人馬座|人馬座]]。天文學家於2008年觀測到該行星的母恆星[[OGLE-2006-BLG-109L|OGLE-2006-BLG-109L]]的[[微引力透镜|微引力透镜]]現象，而發現了該行星與另一顆行星[[OGLE-2006-BLG-109Lc|OGLE-2006-BLG-109Lc]]<ref name="disc">{{cite journal | url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/319/5865/927 | title=Discovery of a Jupiter/Saturn Analog with Gravitational Microlensing | journal=[[科学_(期刊)|Science]] | volume=319 | issue=5865 | year=2008 | pages=927–930 | doi=10.1126/science.1151947 | pmid=18276883 | last1=Gaudi | first1=B. S. | first2=B.S. | last2=Bennett | first3=DP | last3=Udalski | last4=Gould | first4=A | last5=Christie | first5=GW | last6=Maoz | first6=D | last7=Dong | first7=S | last8=McCormick | first8=J | last9=Szymanski | first9=MK | display-authors=1 | bibcode=2008Sci...319..927G | arxiv=0802.1920 | access-date=2016-09-27 | archive-date=2010-05-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531174150/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/319/5865/927 | dead-url=no }} [http://arxiv.org/abs/0802.1920 web preprint] {{Wayback|url=http://arxiv.org/abs/0802.1920 |date=20170204004923 }}</ref>。

